  "Briefing Objective": "Review and analyze key drivers of electricity \u0026 fuel prices at various regional markets throughout North America, with a special emphasis on those subregions of the Eastern Grids.   "ERCOT Market": "EPMI personnel have a wealth of experience in working in ISO Markets.  It is our feeling that the ERCOT market, which opens July 20, will provide [Forney, John M.]  significant   opportunity in maximizing value for Frontera.   [Forney, John M.]      Opportunity should lie within the Balancing Market [Forney, John M.]  ,   Ancillary Services Market [Forney, John M.]   and the decremental bidding \"market.\"  [Forney, John M.]  Immediate plans will include submitting decremental bids into the ISO.   We will be responsible for responding to the ISO instructions by decreasing the output from Frontera during key hours.",
